<materialsCitation id="77D8475BFFB6FF85FC2D261EFC3E8C73" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3037467333" pageId="37" pageNumber="37">11 females (AMNH *265963, *265965, *267058, *267060, *267377, *267379, *267842; MNHN *1995.847, *1995.848, *1995.849, *1995.850) and 11 males (AMNH *265962, 265964, *265966, *267057, *267064, *267374, *267378, *267840; MNHN *1995.851, *1995.852, *1995.853); see table 8 for measurements. One individual of unknown sex (AMNH 266977) was recovered from the crop of a bat falcon.</materialsCitation>
